social_posts.post_text: ‘Promise?’ liquid acrylic on Arches watercolor paper, 11”x16”. This painting is headed for Canada, thanks @dimitriu1
‘Black Rose of Death’  Liquid Acrylic and Ink on Arches watercolor paper  13”x24”. This painting comes framed and is available to own.
Fiji Mermaid, liquid acrylic on Arches watercolor paper, 11”x17”. This painting is available on my webshop.

“Worry” 
liquid acrylic on Arches watercolor paper, 23”x23” framed.
Worrying is like carrying your own coffin throughout life. I really love this Italian hand carved frame, and was saving it for something special. We’ve all had the burden of overwhelming dread, which can feel like this image. This one is available to own too!
Went with some limited color on this one, just black, bright red and raw umber. I have this original 11”x17” flash sheet up on my webshop too!

Filet Mignon, New York Strip and Tomahawks. Made some more Beef cuts since y’all were digging the Meat Sheet. All three of these are 8”x10” on oval panels, all very reasonably priced too, available you know where.
Piña colada, acrylic on round 10” panel. I’ve been working on some fun paintings lately, just stuff that makes me happy. This one is available for your collection too! #pinacolada #cocktail
Some sweet treats for you all, “Neapolitan”, “Red Velvet”, “Space Race” and “Key Lime”. All available through my webshop.

“Old World” 
Acrylic on Wooden panel, 10”x20”. This painting is available too!

My son turned 20 yesterday, we hung out all day and tattooed this on him, seems like he was just a baby not too long ago, now here he is sitting like a champ for a 4 hour tattoo. Love you Jaes McDonald!

I painted this for a machine trade with @dminus12 , thanks for the swap Dustin, I love the liner and shader I got from you! Liquid acrylic on Arches paper.
I always love painting roses, I try to find new ways to study and improve on them. They’re liquid acrylic on Arches paper. These 3 are  all available on my web shop.
“Kitsune” liquid acrylic on Arches paper, 8.5”x12”, thanks for looking!

“Death Dive”
Liquid acrylic on Arches watercolor paper, 14”x20”. This painting is available through my webshop.

Thorns, 100 page book of all new sketches & outlines of roses, leaves, thorns, stems, sprigs and rosebuds! Softcover 9”x12”, printed on vanilla cream pages.
I’ve dedicated more than half of my life to drawing, tattooing and painting roses, studying both classical and new techniques to improve on them. This book is an inside look at how I construct and develop tattoo rose anatomy. All books are available through my site!
Time lapse of “The Ghost Of Oiwa”, a shorter version of a liquid acrylic painting tutorial I made for @aidanwaterstattoo .

social_posts.post_text: “Lysergic Flowers”  Liquid Acrylic on Arches watercolor paper, 18”x24”. Available on my site!

All pre-orders of “Thorns” have been shipped! We had some delays with the original publisher, but these turned out gloriously! Beautiful matte cover, 100 pages pages printed into a large 9”x12” professionally bound book. Each page was specifically drawn for this book, with over 250 new roses I’ve been saving for the project. Use them as is, or change them to your own vision. Now available!
“Hunting The Crawling Shadows”, acrylic on wooden panel, 12”x18”, available on my webshop!
“Incantation” Acrylic on wooden coffin shaped panel, 9”x16”. This painting is available too!
“Unseen” Acrylic on wooden shaped coffin panel, 9”x16”, got a little weird with this one, it’s available too.

“The Killing Moon, Will Come Too Soon”
Acrylic on oval canvas panel, 12”x16”. This painting is available for your collection too!
“Shrunken Head”, acrylic on oval canvas, 8”x10”. I’ve been wanting to paint one of these for awhile now, it’s available too!
Wild Roses, liquid acrylic on Arches watercolor, 14”x17”. This larger sized sheet is available through my webshop too!

Teaser trailer for one of my newest short films “Yokai Terror”, about a father hellbent on revenge against creatures and spirits responsible for his daughters disappearance. This film is heavily inspired by Japanese horror and mythology, and will be part of an Amazon episodic series along with a few of our other new films. I wrote, produced and directed this project, and I’m really proud of the work that my team @devilredfilms created. Yokai Terror’s dialogue is completely spoken in Japanese, with English subtitles, coming 2024!

Teaser trailer for another horror film I made over the summer.
“Shroud Of Satan” 
A widow fears her body and soul are under the behest of Satan, after futile attempts of exorcism, she’s forced to seek out the wisdom of occultists against her own faith. 
I wrote, produced and directed this short film with my team @devilredfilms , it’ll be part of a series on Amazon next spring.
“Sentry” Acrylic on wooden panel, 11”x14” this painting is available, thanks for looking!
“Spirit In The Bamboo Forest” this one is 12”x24”, available on my site. #japaneseghost #yurei
“Game Of Death” Acrylic on wooden panel, 12”x16”, this one is for sale on my site, as are a few others I haven’t posted yet 😎)

Recently painted this series of fish on some smaller canvas panels, would make great gifts, 150 each.

My painting for the “Momento Mori” book from the great folks @blackdaggerbooks , 94 paintings by some incredible artists in tattooing. Preorder your copy of this one! This painting is also for sale. Thanks for lookin’!

@mcdonaldmagnetic of @magnetictattoo will take part in “Steeped in Tradition” tattoo art exhibition. Their artwork will be on display for viewing and purchase at @goldenstagkc. Opening January 14, 2024 and running thru February 25, 2024. Please join us at the opening. Your presence is appreciated.
Getting over being sick the last few weeks, but I’ve been finishing up  a bunch of big ol’ oil paintings that I can’t wait to finally show y’all.

“Black Swan”
Oil on wooden panel, 18”x24” (24”x32” framed). This painting is available and comes with this lovely frame. #rococo

“Cruel Heart Of Winter”
Oil on wooden panel, 12”x24” (17”x30” framed), this painting is available!

“Standing On The Devils Backbone” 
Oil on Canvas, 36”x 48” 
This resilient Bison has made its final stand atop a cliff at Devils Backbone in Northern Colorado, no doubt it’s hunters are not far behind. This painting is available! #classicalpainting #bison #devilsbackbone #lovelandcolorado #buffalo #landscapepainting #landseer
Just wanna give a huge thank you, and I’m grateful to all of you that have supported me this year, y’all make the old lad feel loved. Hope this next year shines on you! ❤️🙏
